Package: chatAI4R
Type: Package
Title: Chat-based Artificial Intelligence for R
Version: 0.0.2
Date: 2023-07-12
Authors@R: c(person("Satoshi", "Kume", 
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "satoshi.kume.1984@gmail.com"))
Description: chatAI4R provides a seamless interface for integrating 
    OpenAI and other APIs into R. It utilizes the ChatGPT API 
    (see <https://platform.openai.com/docs/api-reference>) for natural 
    language processing, making it ideal for efficient data analysis and 
    knowledge discovery. Additionally, it includes functionalities for executing 
    bioinformatics analysis methods, making it a versatile tool for a variety of research domains.
Depends: R (>= 4.2.0)
Imports: xml2, httr, jsonlite, magrittr, purrr, rvest, stringr, assertthat, 
    clipr, crayon, remotes, EBImage, grDevices, hexSticker, abind
Suggests: testthat
License: Artistic-2.0
URL: https://github.com/kumeS/chatAI4R
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
